;/p&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td width="12"&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;td valign="bottom" width="28"&gt;&lt;img alt="立即收听" height="28" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/ihClwsFiKu8o/v0/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; border-radius: 10px;" width="28" /&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;随着赛事规模和碳排放量的增加，气候变化正在影响体育运动，体育运动也在影响气候。本周的《零》节目中，阿克沙特·拉蒂 (Akshat Rathi) 与北卡罗来纳大学教授杰西卡·默弗里 (Jessica Murfree) 一起参加了节目，杰西卡·默弗里致力于研究体育与气候变化的交叉点。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/KrNUNqLv_lbaRmDoCiJvNp1INtixPSoMQmUFE4LxSgg_oMmvN-damX3hq2luHSfeFKXPauAbs9q7PY9c5F3ZfimeR_OcNV4X_XgLnN64W6CCx7JQA86oP1nUKseFU04-OvL735s8IhKoZCmdR4fu0E_5FT3f25svP6yw04T9nEDmnLdgW0DGm6PA47knBxIYJOU-BTsFiNKMm1Fkszh2qxIuXX2lZG1wNSq9E8DP70rB3bpFt3rHvsIz4G_8DdDu3I-BloEMaFV0RY9HHALFK1c1AJZaw-WnS-xN7Xc3Eh-UGMEyLZriD9rTtAgJAfGYkBhaOAVs02Ouzbo2lv6EQyTiVPDtkQc/Z-yZoIIx7OnArv7_Smp0VqyT9XggZqtF/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="世界是否变得太热，不适合夏季运动？ - 零"&gt;立即收听&lt;/a&gt;，并在&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/rWkc2av3vKKG9-8s_410ILN_iZQ9On9tkl51-Dr4ls13XLxnBcitSeGp7WY9Vb84jA_Si5Iu0mNFyXM5yjww5SOASmcdZTR0JaPPnN9tie40XKOKVXImZZuOhSekrHMb08lTlw9IFNhKBOc8Uj1ZVzy2P0i-fVMQiV9MqztrCqyfn7mlHPbf-FlXhg7-lIBEBPrjKrrqiITMrDPW3VYKPGATw5hS79f23DygCk8bsIdfOTAZs2j1IeqMJM57bE14OkZSFrlArJbMl2lXSlgFMyQkPC_w6tRyJyQFqoQmCljG1t9pS4u55FWtm3939zeWc1qJKg/QaPWoBjyOdom5iNdPzTWmS2Gy5UQ0M8x/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="零：气候竞赛"&gt;Apple&lt;/a&gt; 、 &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/eMqA4KflOnLPQBlSGprhy_ZaJa3fiTkbyEJvdreTXYxnB7Hd96GEbMG9_9WtoFrvFg3hJmtp9h7YEqNibRv6cg9rtalBqIkeLopGm3BgvfI9R5m_nwZSwxHZ4-5OM9G5O4v5U64gNGdY58AhboUzxqcFB-gyRht89O5iy_be7-JdQmTOEtjZSvuHoCHZTNiJfRJuoA9ZT9QbQxCFMKUngu_SVjga1qI5Kmzd-iaQ3wguk_BSsebkYMmuVHmyTuUCxYdbD_hZnZQCdIyev4sS